    "updated_at": "2016-05-06T10:46:47Z",
    "body": "Unfortunately Chromium just writes everything to `userData` directory, the logic is hard-coded everywhere and it is impossible to easily patch it. Plus we have removed the `userCache` directory from `getPath`, so I'm closing this as won't fix.\n"
